<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>
@EM{{@HI{{bakari ka}} ... @HI{{sae}}}} is a compound particle which carries the meaning of "not only ... but also".
The item that precedes @EM{{@HI{{bakari ka}}}} is something that is normally to be expected and whatever follows
is something that normally would be unexpected.
</p>

<p>
In speech @EM{{@HI{{sae}}}} can be replaced by @HI{{mo}}.
</p>

